    "description": "<strong>Games Gallery</strong> is a game without basic mechanics, and without belonging to any genre. In this game you will be placed in a virtual gallery of games developed by &quot;<strong>Piece Of Voxel</strong>&quot;.  Along which you can walk yourself in 3-D.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209570/extras/f469606c2e970f847371c5cbecd4fefb.avif?t=1668546927\" width=600 height=244 /></span><br>Each game is presented in the form of several paintings and interactive objects, such as a mini-mechanism, a machine or a teleporter.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209570/extras/9bacf5a5d5d9fac3443deaf7fb89f061.avif?t=1668546927\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br>In the game you will have access to more than 20 different stands with games, each of which will have a mini description and history of its creation, as well as a large number of Easter eggs hidden throughout the game map.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209570/extras/35a17654239c03c181dca1bbd11b4d50.avif?t=1668546927\" width=600 height=268 /></span><br>With this game, you can get a closer look at the &quot;<strong>Piece Of Voxel</strong>&quot; games before buying them, for example, get acquainted with the visual style of each of the games in 3-D, and not just see screenshots and a trailer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209570/extras/3e1e7b0f464edd2b5e22d91cf209eb91.avif?t=1668546927\" width=600 height=280 /></span>",
